manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Bring Me in When You Are Having a Long Journey or Trip Worldwide? You are leaving your office for a business trip worldwide. So you put your computer, iPad, camera and other electronic products in your backpack. Worry that you may lack of outlets for your devices, you grab the round donut shaped power strip on your desk. In your long journey, you take photos,make phone calls, talk about business. All your devices are running out of power. You arrived at a hotel for a short rest, looking around, only to find there is ONE outlet on the wall, and you have a lot of products which need to charge. What will you do? You used a voltage converter (the unit itself does not convert voltage) and take out the 'donut' from your bag, and your 'low battery'devices are perfectly handled. It is so lightweight and well fit for your business trip.

'I Know Exactly the Optimal Current You Have Long Been Looking for' 3 USB Charging Ports are all equipped with smart IC which can intelligently deliver proper current according to different devices up to 5V 2.4A per port. It’s compatible with 5V usb device, like phone, tablet, MP3, MP4, Bluetooth and other digital devices. The Max output is 2.4A for each port, 3A 15W total. It can charge 3 phones at the same time and not effect the charging speed, like the original charger for your device. Specifications: -Power rating: 1250W (125V 10A) -USB power rating: 15W (5V 3A) -USB port input: AC 100-240V 50/60HZ

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great for travel
reviews.reviewText: We took this to Disney and it was perfect for charging MagicBands. Packs well and works great. The cord is a little short, but long enough to use on a table or counter top. Will bring this with us on every trip!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 31, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to take on trips. It’s perfect. Doesn’t take up much space in the suitcase, durable and makes an awesome charging station for what we need.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 7, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Well made, clever design, 3 USB, 3 Three-Prong Outlets, Perfect for Countertop
reviews.reviewText: I liked that it had a combination of USB and regular 3-prong outlets, a compact round flat shape, and that it is easily accessible on my peninsula counter (where I like to charge my devices). The cord is about 15 inches long which is perfect for where I’m using it, but too short to use on my office desk. Would be nice to offer a variety of lengths. Making the product with an adjustable cord might make it too large. As is, the size is small enough to not take up significant counter space. I highly recommend this product for Countertop Charging. Caveat: I have only been using the product for 1 week; seems to be perfect 🤞

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 17, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The cord was to short but I make it work use it for travel because I travel 4 day a week and stay at hotel and most the time don’t have enough plugs in the room. Great for travel would buy again but need a long cord.
